---
import Base from "@/layouts/Base.astro";

import { getEntry } from "astro:content";

const highwaysproject = await getEntry("high-ways-project", "-index");

import { SEO } from "astro-seo";
---
<SEO
  title="Edhi Foundation High Way Project - Road Safety and Aid"
  description="Learn about Edhi Foundation's High Way Project. Promoting road safety and providing emergency aid on highways."
  canonical={Astro.request.url}
  openGraph={{
    basic: {
      title: "Edhi Foundation High Way Project - Road Safety and Aid",
      type: "A type.",
      image: "https://edhiuk.org/images/logo.jpg",
   
    }
  }}
  twitter={{
    creator: "@jonasmerlins1"
  }}
  extend={{
    // extending the default link tags
    link: [{ rel: "icon", href: "/favicon.png" }],
    // extending the default meta tags
    meta: [
      {
        name: "twitter:image",
        content: "https://edhiuk.org/images/logo.jpg",
      },
      { name: "twitter:title", content: "Edhi Foundation High Way Project - Road Safety and Aid" },
      { name: "twitter:description", content: "Learn about Edhi Foundation's High Way Project. Promoting road safety and providing emergency aid on highways." },
      { name: "keywords", content: "" },
    ],
  }}
/>

<Base >
   <!-- head started here -->

   <section class="relative bg-green-50 dark:bg-gray-900/30 pt-0">
    <div
      class="mx-auto lg:max-w-7xl w-full px-5 sm:px-10 md:px-12 lg:px-5 relative"
    >
      <div
        class="absolute left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 lg:-translate-x-[28px] lg:-translate-y-[40px] lg:left-0 lg:top-16 w-40 h-40 skew-x-6 opacity-50 dark:opacity-80 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-bl from-green-600 to-green-600/70 blur-xl flex"
      >
      </div>

      <div
        class="flex text-center lg:text-left flex-col lg:items-center lg:flex-row gap-8 lg:gap-10 xl:gap-12 relative max-w-4xl lg:max-w-none"
      >
        <div class="space-y-8 xl:space-y-10 lg:py-12 flex-1 xl:w-1/2">
          <h1
            class="text-black dark:text-white text-3xl/tight sm:text-4xl/tight md:text-5xl/tight xl:text-[50px] font-bold"
          >
          Highway <span
              class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-br from-[#14A762] to-[#14A762]"
            >
            Project <br> (25 kilometer)</span
            >
          </h1>
          <p
            class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-md mx-auto lg:max-w-none font-roboto text-[17]"
          >
          The Highway Project aims to establish five hundred Edhi Centres along Pakistan's highways and major link roads. These centres provide first aid to accident victims, medical facilities in rural areas, and other welfare services, ensuring swift assistance to those in need.          </p>
          <div
            class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4 z-30 sm:w-max sm:flex-nowrap mx-auto lg:mx-0"
          >
            <a
              href="https://donate.edhiuk.org/"
              class="px-5 h-12 flex items-center sm:w-max w-full justify-center bg-[#14A762] text-white rounded-lg ease-linear transition"
            >
              DONATE NOW
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          aria-hidden="true"
          class="flex-1 lg:w-1/2 relative hidden lg:flex justify-end pr-8 w-1/2"
        >
          <img
            src="/images/zakat.jpg"
            class="relative rounded"
            alt="portrait-of-smiling-medical-worker-girl-doctor"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <!-- head ended here -->
  <!-- section 1 started -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row px-6  py-10">
    <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 pr-6">
      <h3 class="text-4xl text-left pb-2">Comprehensive Medical Services</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
      <p class="text-justify font-roboto text-[17] ">
        Each Edhi Centre under the Highway Project is equipped with three ambulances, a four-bedded emergency unit, a permanent dispensary, and a mobile dispensary. These centres provide medical assistance to approximately two hundred and fifty patients daily, offering vital healthcare services to rural and semi-urban communities.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section >
    <!-- section 1 ended -->

    <!-- section 2 started -->
<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
  <div class="md:text-center text-left pb-16">
    <h3 class="text-black text-4xl font-bold pb-2">
      Expansion and   <span class="text-green-600">Development</span>
    </h3>

    <div class="sm:grid-cols-1">
      <div class="md:text-center text-left mb-4">
        <p class=" font-roboto text-[17]">
          The Highway Project also includes the establishment of additional Edhi Homes for the destitute, dispensaries, centres for the rehabilitation of heroin addicts, ambulance centres, and rural welfare centres. Efforts are underway to acquire additional ambulance aircraft to enhance the speed and efficiency of service delivery between these centres.
        </p><br />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
  <!-- section 2 ended -->
</Base>
